<section id="h21002">
<title>
<emphasis id="Program_operation" effect="bold">

Program operation

</emphasis>


</title>




<para id="p1013">
When the user clicks the green flag, the values of the slider variables shown in


<link id="a1051" target-id="Image_1">

Image 1

</link>

 are set to 0. Expressions containing relational 
operators are evaluated to set the values of the bottom three variables to the 
boolean values of true or false.

</para>




<para id="p1014">
The user slides the two sliders to change the values of 

<emphasis id="strong1010" effect="bold">
LeftOperand

</emphasis>
 and


<emphasis id="strong1011" effect="bold">
RightOperand

</emphasis>
.

</para>




<para id="p1015">
When the user clicks the button at the bottom of 

<link id="a1052" target-id="Image_1">

Image 1

</link>

, three separate event handlers on the button 
test the left operand against the right operand for 

<emphasis id="em1011" effect="italics">
less than

</emphasis>
, 

<emphasis id="em1012" effect="italics">
equal 
to

</emphasis>
, and 

<emphasis id="em1013" effect="italics">
greater than

</emphasis>
 and display string values describing the results in the three variables 
having the corresponding names in 

<link id="a1053" target-id="Image_1">

Image 1

</link>

 and 


<link id="a1054" target-id="Image_2">

Image 2

</link>

. Those three event handlers are 
shown as the bottom three scripts in the programming panel of


<link id="a1055" target-id="Image_3">

Image 3

</link>

.

</para>




</section>
</section>
