<emphasis id="em1035" effect="italics">
equal to

</emphasis>
, and 

<emphasis id="em1036" effect="italics">
greater than

</emphasis>
 and display the results in the three 
variables having the corresponding names as either true or false. 

</para>




<para id="p1059">
